JOHANNESBURG - Western Cape MEC for Social Development Albert Fritz has been attacked in Nyanga on Saturday morning.Fritz and two bodyguards were outside the Assembly of God Church when two men reportedly robbed them at gunpoint of two cellphones. Fritz spoke about the ordeal:One suspect was shot dead and the other injured.READ: DA councillor shot dead in Cape TownA bystander was also injured.Cape Town mayoral committee member JP Smith gave more details:eNCA